==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stapler
<hw>Sta"pler</hw> <pr>(-pl⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A dealer in staple goods.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One employed to assort wool according to its
staple.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A device used to drive a staple{8} into objects so
as to fasten them together.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Star</ent>⟦br⟧
